    #include <iostream>
    #include <ctime>

    inline void calculateAge(int birthYear, int birthMonth, int currentYear, int currentMonth, int &years, int &months) {
    if (currentMonth >= birthMonth) {
    years = currentYear - birthYear;
    months = currentMonth - birthMonth;
    } else {
    years = currentYear - birthYear - 1;
    months = 12 - birthMonth + currentMonth;
    }
    }

    int main() {
    int birthYear, birthMonth;
    int currentYear, currentMonth;

    std::cout << "Enter birth year and month: ";
    std::cin >> birthYear >> birthMonth;

    std::cout << "Enter current year and month: ";
    std::cin >> currentYear >> currentMonth;

    int years, months;
    calculateAge(birthYear, birthMonth, currentYear, currentMonth, years, months);

    std::cout << "Age: " << years << " years and " << months << " months." << std::endl;

    return 0;
    }
